        "<p>â€œHe has to telephone,â€ said Mr. Wolfshiem, following him with his</p>\n<p>eyes. â€œFine fellow, isnâ€™t he? Handsome to look at and a perfect</p>\n<p>gentleman.â€</p>\n<p>â€œYes.â€</p>\n<p>â€œHeâ€™s an Oggsford man.â€</p>\n<p>â€œOh!â€</p>\n<p>â€œHe went to Oggsford College in England. You know Oggsford College?â€</p>",
