        "<p>â€œCome on!â€ His temper cracked a little. â€œWhatâ€™s the matter, anyhow?</p>\n<p>If weâ€™re going to town, letâ€™s start.â€</p>\n<p>His hand, trembling with his effort at self-control, bore to his lips</p>\n<p>the last of his glass of ale. Daisyâ€™s voice got us to our feet and out</p>\n<p>on to the blazing gravel drive.</p>\n<p>â€œAre we just going to go?â€ she objected. â€œLike this? Arenâ€™t we going</p>\n<p>to let anyone smoke a cigarette first?â€</p>",
